===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Internet]] [[Protocol]]'''

# {{internet}} The [[computer]] [[networking]] [[protocol|protocols]] that are anticedents or decendents of the [[IETF]] STD005 "INTERNET PROTOCOL", characterized by being [[packet-switching|packet-switched]], [[unreliable]], and [[connectionless]]; especially the most widely used protocol, [[IPv4]].

